<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="moving-text" style="padding: 22px; color:black">
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <div class="text-center p-3">
      <h1 class="bordered-div" style="color:blue">Welcome to Banking App (All banks in one app)</h1> </div>
      <br>
       <h1><strong>Number of Accounts:</strong> <%= @account_count %></h1><br>
       <% if @banks.present? %>
    <div>
      <h1><strong>Your Accounts based in these Banks :</strong></h1>
      <ul>
        <% @banks.each do |bank| %>
          <li><h3> 
          <a href="<%= bank_path(bank) %>"style="text-decoration:none; color:blue">
          <%= bank.bank_name %>
          </a>
           </h3></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <p>No accounts found.</p>
  <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <div class="bordered-div" >
      <h1 class="moving-text" style="color: black">Welcome to Banking App (All banks in one app)</h1>
      <p class="moving-text" style="color: black">
        Manage your finances with ease.
        In this rapidly evolving digital era, the world of banking has undergone a profound transformation. Gone are the days of long queues, 
        complex paperwork, and limited accessibility.
        With the advent of innovative technologies, banking has become more streamlined, efficient, and customer-centric.
        One such groundbreaking innovation is the ultimate banking app, a game-changer in the financial industry.
        This blog aims to explore the features and benefits of this revolutionary banking app, highlighting how it 
        facilitates users and enhances their banking experience.
        <br>The ultimate banking app represents a significant leap forward in the world of banking, 
        revolutionizing how users interact with their finances. <br>With its seamless account management,
        secure transactions, personalized insights, exceptional customer support, 
        robust security features, and integration with third-party services, 
        this app is a game-changer in the industry. By placing the power of banking in users' 
        hands, it empowers individuals to take control of their financial well-being and achieve 
        their financial goals. As we embrace the digital future, the ultimate banking app stands at the forefront, 
        redefining banking convenience and setting new standards for customer-centric financial services.<br>
        </p> <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Log In", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %></div>
      
    <% end %>
</div>
